      <title>SonntagsZeitung 称瑞银将于 6 月开始五波裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/five-waves-ubs-layoffs-start-june-sonntagszeitung-says-2024-04-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《星期日报》周日报道，瑞士银行业巨头瑞银集团在收购瑞信后宣布的成本削减计划将于今年六月开始分五波进行裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/five-waves-ubs-layoffs-start-june-sonntagszeitung-says-2024-04-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 09:53:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
