      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，美国监管机构正在考虑限制华尔街高管的奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-regulators-mulling-bid-limit-bonuses-wall-street-execs-wsj-reports-2024-04-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》周五报道，美国银行业监管机构正计划重启一项提案，要求大型银行推迟高管薪酬，并在亏损扩大时收回更多奖金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-regulators-mulling-bid-limit-bonuses-wall-street-execs-wsj-reports-2024-04-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 17:51:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
